# API keys for the live-data integrations. Copy this file to .env.local and
# fill in the keys you have. .env.local is git-ignored; Vite inlines VITE_*
# variables into the client bundle at build time.
#
# Note: anything inlined into the bundle is visible to anyone viewing the
# deployed page's source. That's fine for a Demo-tier key on an internal
# tool; for a public production deploy, proxy the calls through a backend.

# CoinGecko Demo — live + historical prices.
# https://www.coingecko.com/en/developers/dashboard
VITE_COINGECKO_API_KEY=

# CoinMarketCap Pro — token logos (animated GIFs for top tokens, static PNG
# fallback). Optional: TokenIcon falls back to CryptoRank / jsdelivr if blank.
# https://pro.coinmarketcap.com/account
VITE_COINMARKETCAP_API_KEY=

# CryptoRank — backup token-image source + manager funding-round data.
# Optional: image fallbacks degrade silently, manager Rounds tab shows a
# "no API key configured" message.
# https://cryptorank.io/api
VITE_CRYPTORANK_API_KEY=
